casebody.data:
Kenneth R. Squires, Respondent, v. Vincent Klein, Appellant, et al., Defendant.

Judgment and order affirmed, with costs. All concur. (Appeal from a judgment of Cayuga Trial Term for plaintiff and against defendant Klein, in an automobile negligence action. The order denied a motion for a new trial.)

Present — McCurn, P. J., Kimball, Williams, Bastow and Goldman, JJ.
